Lineage and acknowledgment

OpenH2O is an independent, clean-room reimplementation on an open stack
(Django, GeoDjango, PostgreSQL/PostGIS, Docker). It descends conceptually from
the Groundwater Accounting Platform stewarded by the California Water Data
Consortium and developed by ESA (formerly Sitka Technology Group), which is
likewise released under the GNU Affero General Public License v3. We are
grateful for that prior art. No ESA/Sitka source code is included in this
repository.
